{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"scroll","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>El evento <strong><code>scroll</code></strong> se produce cuando la vista del documento o un elemento es deslizado.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"información_general","title":"Información General","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"especificación\">Especificación</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events/#event-type-scroll\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM L3</a>, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/cssom-view/#scrolling-0\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSSOM View</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interfaz\">Interfaz</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">UIEvent</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No en elementos, pero burbujea a la vista default cuando se ejecuta&nbsp;en el documento</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"objetivo\">Objetivo</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">defaultView, Document, Element</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"acción_por_defecto\">Acción por defecto</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Ninguna</dd>\n <dt style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 120px;\" id=\"sect1\"></dt>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propiedades","title":"Propiedades","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\" title=\"EventTarget is an interface implemented by objects that can receive events and may have listeners for them.\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>El objetivo de evento (el objetivo superior en el árbol DOM).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\" title=\"DOMString is a UTF-16 String. As JavaScript already uses such strings, DOMString is mapped directly to a String.\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>El tipo de evento.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\" title=\"The Boolean object is an object wrapper for a boolean value.\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Si el evento burbujea o no.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\" title=\"The Boolean object is an object wrapper for a boolean value.\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Si el evento puede ser cancelado o no.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>view</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"new page-not-created\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WindowProxy\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>WindowProxy</code></a></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/defaultView\" title=\"In browsers, document.defaultView returns the window object associated with a document, or null if none is available.\"><code>document.defaultView</code></a> (<code>window</code> de el documento)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>detail</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><code>long</code> (<code>float</code>)</td>\n   <td>0.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dado que los eventos <code>scroll</code> pueden ejecutarse&nbsp;a un ritmo elevado, el <em>event handler</em> no debería ejecutar operaciones computacionalmente costosas como modificaciones en el DOM. En cambio, se recomienda acelerar el evento utilizando <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/window/requestAnimationFrame\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/window.requestAnimationFrame\">requestAnimationFrame</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\">setTimeout</a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\">customEvent</a>, de este modo:</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"optimización_de_scroll_con_window.requestanimationframe\">Optimización de Scroll con window.requestAnimationFrame</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Referencia: http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/speed/animations/</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> last_known_scroll_position <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ticking <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">doSomething</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">scroll_pos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Hacer algo con la posición del scroll</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'scroll'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  last_known_scroll_position <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollY<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>ticking<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">requestAnimationFrame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">doSomething</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>last_known_scroll_position<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      ticking <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  ticking <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Más ejemplos se pueden ver en el evento <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/resize_event#example\">resize</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibilidad_en_navegadores","title":"Compatibilidad en navegadores","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ios_uiwebview","title":"iOS UIWebView","isH3":true,"content":"<p>En iOS UIWebViews, los eventos <code>scroll</code> no se ejecutan mientras el <em>escroleo/deslizamiento</em> se lleva a cabo; solo son ejecutados cuando el deslizamiento terminó. Ver <a href=\"https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/issues/16202\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bootstrap issue #16202</a>. Safari y WKWebViews no se ven afectados por este bug.</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Información General","id":"información_general"},{"text":"Propiedades","id":"propiedades"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Compatibilidad en navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_en_navegadores"}],"summary":"El evento scroll se produce cuando la vista del documento o un elemento es deslizado.","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document: scroll event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"scroll","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document: scroll event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"scroll","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Document: событие scroll","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document: scroll event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document: scroll事件","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/document/scroll_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/document/scroll_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event","title":"scroll"}],"pageTitle":"scroll - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}